  <body>
    <div xml:id="PN321-intro">
      <p type="edition">tiṇaiyum tuṟaiyum avai. uṟaiyūr maruttuvaṉ tāmōtaraṉār.
      </p>
      <p xml:lang="en" type="translation">  
      </p>
